" Standard Emacs navigation
imap <C-p> <Up>
imap <C-n> <Down>
imap <C-b> <Left>
imap <C-f> <Right>

imap <A-b> <C-Left>
imap <A-f> <C-Right>

" Duplicate the same to command line mode
cmap <C-p> <Up>
cmap <C-n> <Down>
cmap <C-b> <Left>
cmap <C-f> <Right>

cmap <A-b> <C-Left>
cmap <A-f> <C-Right>

" Reopen closed tabs
nmap <S-x> <C-S-t>
